Package it.unicam.cs.pa.jbudget105101.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Bank
    Le classi che implementeranno Bank avranno la responsabilità di implementare un gestore di CashBox.
    CashBox
    The classes that will implement CashBox will have the responsibility to implement what will later be "money boxes".
    Category
    A Category has the responsibility to represents a type in which a Transaction can be part.
    CategoryManager
    A CategoryManager represents a manager who has the responsibility to manage a collection of Category.
    IdentificationManager<T extends Identifier<?>>
    A manager has a responsibility to manage and create new identifiers.
    Identifier<T>
    An {code Identifier} is responsible for representing an identification code.
    Transaction
    Le classi che implementeranno Transaction avranno la responsabilit&agrave; di implementare un movimento.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicTransaction
    La classe BasicTransaction rappresenta un singolo movimento.
    Box
    A Box will have the function of managing a list of Transactions by storing the balance, the money spent and the money earned.
    DebitBox
    The DebitBox class represents a LoadBox with an interval that starts from the goal and ends at zero.
    FamilyBank
    La classe FamilyBank rappresenta un gestore di CashBox.
    IntegerId
    An IntegerId represents an identification code consisting of an int type number.
    IntegerIdManager
    An Integer Manager represents a manager who manages Integer Identifiers.
    LoadBox
    The LoadBox class extends the functionality of a Box allowing you to define a range in which the balance must be included.
    SaveBox
    The SaveBox class represents a LoadBox with an interval that starts from zero up to the target set.
    Tag
    The Tag class represents a category of a Transaction}.
    TagManager
    The TagManager class represents a manager who manages a Set of Category.
    Wallet
    A Wallet will have the function of managing a list of Transactions by storing the balance, the money spent and the money earned.
